title: Ep. - 290 - NFL ROOKIE BREIDEN FEHOKO FROM HARDKNOCKS ON HBO THIS IS PARIS
description:
National Football League rookie Breiden Fehoko from the Los Angeles Chargers talks about this season of Hard Knocks on HBO, what it has been like training during Covid, and how much it has meant to him having so many people embrace his Polynesian culture. This season of Hard Knocks gives an unfiltered all-access look at what it takes to make it in the National Football League. The 18-time Sports Emmy Award winning series follows head coaches Anthony Lynn of the Los Angeles Chargers and Sean McVay of the Los Angeles Rams as they lead a mix of established veterans, free-agent acquisitions, and rising stars on both sides of the ball.

 

Gibson Johns helps Kate review This is Paris, a documentary on Paris Hilton.
